description.original: An Obsidian plugin to paste data from Microsoft Excel, Google Sheets, Apple Numbers and LibreOffice Calc as Markdown tables in Obsidian editor.
description.translation: 一个可将Microsoft Excel, Google Sheets, Apple Numbers 和 LibreOffice Calc的数据在Obsidian编辑器中粘贴为Markdown表格的Obsidian插件
